---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Postmarked">
  <main class="frame py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h1 class="display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lede lede-body text-base">
          Effective Date: May 25, 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8">

        <section class="card-flat">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Welcome to Postmarked ("Postmarked," "we," "our," or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use the Postmarked website and related services.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Postmarked is a private travel-sharing platform that allows users to share travel updates, photos, locations, and trip posts with friends, family, and subscribers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">We may collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Account information such as name, email address, username, and profile details</li>
            <li>Phone numbers used for SMS notifications</li>
            <li>User-generated content including posts, photos, captions, comments, and location information</li>
            <li>Device and browser information</li>
            <li>Log data such as IP address, timestamps, and usage activity</li>
            <li>Communication preferences and notification settings</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">How We Use Information</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">We use collected information to:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Provide and operate the Postmarked service</li>
            <li>Deliver travel updates and notifications requested by users</li>
            <li>Send SMS notifications to users who have explicitly opted in</li>
            <li>Improve the functionality, reliability, and security of the platform</li>
            <li>Respond to support requests and user inquiries</li>
            <li>Prevent abuse, spam, fraud, or unauthorized access</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">SMS Messaging</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Users may voluntarily opt in to receive SMS notifications related to Postmarked updates, including travel posts, location check-ins, and account notifications.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            By opting in, users consent to receive SMS messages from Postmarked. Message frequency varies based on posting activity and account usage. Message and data rates may apply.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Users may opt out at any time by replying STOP, CANCEL, UNSUBSCRIBE, END, QUIT, REVOKE, OPTOUT, or STOPALL. Users may reply HELP for assistance.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Phone numbers collected for SMS notifications are used solely for delivering requested messages and are not sold or shared with third parties except as necessary to provide SMS services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Sharing of Information</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We do not sell personal information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            We may share limited information with third-party service providers that help operate the service, including hosting providers, analytics providers, authentication providers, and SMS delivery providers such as Twilio.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Information may also be disclosed if required by law or to protect the security and integrity of the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We take reasonable measures to protect user information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">User Content</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Users are responsible for the content they upload and share through Postmarked. Users should only share content they have the right to distribute.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Postmarked may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of third-party sites.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Children’s Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Postmarked is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information as soon as possible. If you believe that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, please contact us at support@werehere.app.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes become effective constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            For questions regarding this Privacy Policy, contact:{' '}
            <a href="mailto:support@werehere.app" class="text-ember hover:text-ember-2 transition-colors">support@werehere.app</a>
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-line-soft text-center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">← Back home</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
